curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/10829' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM2046", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM2046 is an ultra-high PSRR, fast transient  response, low noise and low dropout voltage linear  regulator which is designed using CMOS technology. It  provides 1.2A output current capability. The operating  input voltage range is from 0.5V to 5.5V and bias  supply voltage range is from 2.5V to 5.5V. The  adjustable output voltage range is from 0.5V to 3.3V.  Other features include logic-controlled shutdown mode,  short-circuit current limit and thermal shutdown  protection. The SGM2046 has automatic discharge  function to quickly discharge VOUT in the disabled status.  The SGM2046 is available in a Green WLCSP-0.8×1.2-6B-B  package. It operates over an operating temperature range  of -40℃ to +125℃.    "}'
curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/10830' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM2046", "table_name": "FEATURES", "content": "FEATURES  ● Input Supply Voltage Range: 0.5V to 5.5V  ● Bias Supply Voltage Range: 2.5V to 5.5V  ● Adjustable Output Voltage Range: 0.5V to 3.3V  ● Output Voltage Accuracy: ±0.8% at +25℃  ● High PSRR: 68dB (TYP) at 1kHz  ● Low Dropout Voltage: 60mV (TYP) at 1.2A  ● Low Bias Input Current: 35μA (TYP)  ● Very Low Bias Input Current in Shutdown: < 1μA  ● Low Noise: 29μVRMS (TYP)  ● Fast Load Transient Response  ● Output Current Limit  ● Stable with Small Case Size Ceramic Capacitors  ● Thermal Shutdown Protection  ● Logic Level Enable Input for ON/OFF Control  ● -40℃ to +125℃ Operating Temperature Range  ● Available in a Green WLCSP-0.8×1.2-6B-B Package      "}'
